(3) have an ability to support a crew size of at least six persons, unless the
Administrator transmits to the Committee on Science of the House of Rep-
resentatives and the Committee on Commerce, Science, and Transportation
of the Senate not later than 60 days after the date of enactment of this Act,
a report explaining why such a requirement should not be met, the impact
