there  are  some  issues  associated  with  spurious  signals  that  made
the  spacecraft  think  that  it  was  closer  than  what  it  was  and  it
crashed.  I  think  that  that  is,  to  me,  the  thing  that  I  worry  about
the  most,  is  allowing  those  pressures  to  make  one  to  make  some
decision  from  a  systems-engineering  perspective  and  short-change
them.

