MORE CEV BUDGET CONCERNS

I  agree  with  Mr.  Ehlers  that,  certainly,  robotics  is  a  cheaper
method  than  building  things  that  are  capable  of  human  space
flight.  But  I  understand,  Mr.  Horowitz,  and  you  may  correct  me  if
I  am  wrong,  that  this  overall  project  will  include  the  use  of  robot-
