but if I could get it on the record.

Mr.  LI.  Well,  again,  I  understand  that  there  are  a  lot  of  compo-
nents  that  have  been  used  before.  But  as  NASA  will  say  them-
selves,  we  are  talking  about  new  processes.  It  is  new  technology.
